reviewText: I'm a fan of Jean Arthur so perhaps my review is a little biased, but I really enjoyed the movie! It's a great little crime drama, but there are still those few little comedic moments with Jean Arthur.

Terrific movie starring my favorite actor, Joseph Calleia, who was superb, Chester Morris, Jean Arthur, and Lionel Barrymore. Lots of fine acting and action, great story, and totally entertaining. I completely recommend it.
